WEBVTT

00:00:07.371 --> 00:00:10.936
Now when we talk of truth,

00:00:11.811 --> 00:00:18.794
we have to know that the truth is very simple to understand.

00:00:19.685 --> 00:00:24.319
First, we must know the instrument of truth.

00:00:25.076 --> 00:00:26.598
That is,

00:00:26.598 --> 00:00:31.822
you are not this body, this mind, these emotions,

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:38.611
these feelings, these thoughts, but you are the pure Spirit.

00:00:38.998 --> 00:00:41.182
You are the pure Spirit,

00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:43.892
and that has to happen to you

00:00:43.973 --> 00:00:46.762
that you become the Spirit.

00:00:47.118 --> 00:00:51.131
As our heritage has been very sadly,

00:00:51.795 --> 00:00:56.183
we are carrying on many qualities,

00:00:57.041 --> 00:01:00.605
instincts of the animal stage.

00:01:01.016 --> 00:01:05.947
And that’s why we find in people having jealousies and

00:01:05.947 --> 00:01:11.075
oppression, aggression — all kinds of horrifying things.

00:01:11.722 --> 00:01:16.252
Also, the worst part is that man can think.

00:01:16.892 --> 00:01:21.632
And in his awareness, in his thinking, he can also justify

00:01:21.713 --> 00:01:25.137
through his rationality to whatever he is doing.

00:01:25.218 --> 00:01:27.306
So it’s a blind end.

00:01:27.441 --> 00:01:33.084
Once you start justifying to whatever you are doing, it’s a blind end.

00:01:33.622 --> 00:01:37.255
But there is no way through mental exercise

00:01:37.356 --> 00:01:40.364
that you can clear out all these things.

00:01:41.054 --> 00:01:43.733
You must know that your Creator

00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:47.942
has already looked after your self realization.

00:01:48.398 --> 00:01:51.651
He has already made arrangements within you

00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:55.000
to give you your self knowledge.

00:01:55.308 --> 00:01:58.454
So far, you do not know yourself.

00:01:58.555 --> 00:02:00.178
That’s the main thing.

00:02:00.329 --> 00:02:03.605
They have said, know thyself. How? How do we know ourselves?

00:02:03.605 --> 00:02:05.934
We don’t know what we have.

00:02:06.052 --> 00:02:09.504
We know about others, but about ourselves, we don’t know.

00:02:09.622 --> 00:02:13.170
And whatever we know about others is also very superficial.

00:02:13.929 --> 00:02:18.087
So now within us is placed, as I have shown you,

00:02:18.774 --> 00:02:21.417
the power of Kundalini.

00:02:21.535 --> 00:02:25.133
It's called 'Kundal' because it is in three and half coils.

00:02:25.873 --> 00:02:30.967
And it’s a feminine, it’s a feminine power.

00:02:31.337 --> 00:02:33.782
She is your individual mother.

00:02:34.220 --> 00:02:37.685
Everyone has an individual mother.

00:02:38.005 --> 00:02:42.261
And she has tape-recorded all about you,

00:02:42.429 --> 00:02:49.427
about your mistakes,

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:55.328
about what you want, what are your aspirations.

00:02:55.328 --> 00:03:00.689
Everything this mother has recorded within herself.

00:03:01.025 --> 00:03:04.462
Now she's just waiting for the second birth.

00:03:04.849 --> 00:03:09.109
Because it is your own power, you have to get it.

00:03:09.395 --> 00:03:12.532
Sahaja means: 'saha' means with, and 'ja' is born.

00:03:12.727 --> 00:03:17.167
Born with you is the right, is the birthright,

00:03:17.571 --> 00:03:21.778
that you get this yoga, means the union with the divine power.

00:03:22.467 --> 00:03:27.474
Now when I say there is divine power all around us

00:03:27.726 --> 00:03:30.113
and it does all the living work,

00:03:30.524 --> 00:03:34.157
we have to just know that there is a power.

00:03:34.645 --> 00:03:37.031
And everybody has called it by different names.

00:03:37.031 --> 00:03:39.017
Somebody has called it Ruh.

00:03:39.199 --> 00:03:41.675
Somebody has called it Paramchaitanya.

00:03:41.759 --> 00:03:45.139
Somebody has called it the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:03:45.711 --> 00:03:48.165
All this has been on,

00:03:48.401 --> 00:03:50.761
but people don’t know where is that power.

00:03:51.481 --> 00:03:55.973
It is all over which does all the living work.

00:03:56.141 --> 00:03:59.195
You see the beautiful flowers here around.

00:03:59.363 --> 00:04:03.098
Now we never even think how these flowers were created by Mother Earth,

00:04:03.300 --> 00:04:05.724
so beautifully, so differently,

00:04:05.909 --> 00:04:11.944
and how she has put such a beautiful show

00:04:11.944 --> 00:04:15.561
of her kindness, of her patience, of her love.

00:04:16.394 --> 00:04:19.360
Apart from that, if you ask a doctor,

00:04:19.478 --> 00:04:24.269
"Who is the one who runs your heart?"

00:04:24.891 --> 00:04:28.260
He'll say, "It’s the autonomous nervous system."

00:04:28.563 --> 00:04:32.536
Ask the question, "Who is this auto?" He can’t answer.

00:04:33.007 --> 00:04:35.665
They are honest, I must say, they are honest.

00:04:35.833 --> 00:04:38.197
This is what we have to know:

00:04:38.853 --> 00:04:46.796
That all this work, living work, is done without any one of our efforts.

00:04:46.964 --> 00:04:50.481
Effortlessly. And who does that work?

00:04:50.775 --> 00:04:54.168
So this all-pervading power of Divine love,

00:04:54.168 --> 00:04:58.691
which you can call by any name, is around us.

00:04:59.448 --> 00:05:03.085
And it works out everything for us.

00:05:03.623 --> 00:05:06.848
This power knows everything about us.

00:05:07.386 --> 00:05:12.105
Also, it looks after us.

00:05:13.182 --> 00:05:16.252
It guides us.

00:05:17.531 --> 00:05:20.758
It thinks. It organizes.

00:05:21.044 --> 00:05:26.622
But above all, this power loves you.

00:05:32.758 --> 00:05:37.531
Now the time has come for us to rise above human awareness.

00:05:37.884 --> 00:05:41.114
Now how do we become peaceful?

00:05:41.518 --> 00:05:45.000
When you cross this centre, what happens,

00:05:45.305 --> 00:05:48.497
that, like thoughts, they come to us through this centre

00:05:48.884 --> 00:05:50.899
from the past and the future.

00:05:51.017 --> 00:05:55.744
The waves-like thoughts: one, another one, another, like that.

00:05:56.464 --> 00:06:01.698
Now these thoughts, we are jumping on the cusp of these thoughts

00:06:01.967 --> 00:06:06.141
But when Kundalini rises, she elongates those thoughts.

00:06:06.276 --> 00:06:09.659
And what happens to you: That you come in the present.

00:06:09.760 --> 00:06:13.436
No more on the future or the past.

00:06:13.994 --> 00:06:17.124
And there you become completely silent.

00:06:17.410 --> 00:06:21.281
You do not react, but you see everything.

00:06:21.735 --> 00:06:23.519
Just see.

00:06:23.687 --> 00:06:26.061
So you develop a witness state.

00:06:26.196 --> 00:06:28.723
That is the most peaceful state

00:06:28.841 --> 00:06:34.389
by which you can easily achieve the greatest joy.

00:06:34.913 --> 00:06:37.640
For example, now see there's a very beautiful carpet here.

00:06:38.300 --> 00:06:43.560
Now if I look at it in a normal way, I would think, it's a very beautiful carpet,

00:06:43.641 --> 00:06:47.488
how much it will cost, where should I go to buy this and all those things.

00:06:47.569 --> 00:06:53.809
If it’s mine, I'll be more worried. Is it insured or not, what’s happening to the carpet.

00:06:54.078 --> 00:06:58.684
But, after realization, what happens when you look at it?

00:06:59.155 --> 00:07:04.043
The joy of its creation by the artist

00:07:04.043 --> 00:07:05.871
starts bubbling in you.

00:07:06.061 --> 00:07:08.111
And you jump in the ocean,

00:07:08.111 --> 00:07:11.440
jump in the ocean of joy.